                      A. z e. X ( ( z H x ) e. I /\ ( x H z ) e. I ) ) ) ) ) $=
      ( vi wcel cv co wral wa eleq2 cidl cfv cpw crab wss w3a idlval eleq2d crn
      cring c1st fvex eqeltri rnex elpw2 anbi1i wceq raleqbi1dv anbi12d ralbidv
